metadata.name: Crypto Influencer
metadata.description:
"[...] Not being able
to create art
they will not
understand art

They will consider their failure
as creators
only as a failure
of the world

Not being able to love fully
they will believe your love
incomplete
and then they will hate
you

And their hatred will be perfect

Like a shining diamond
Like a knife
Like a mountain
Like a tiger
Like hemlock"
